Hi!  This is Loggerithim.  The documentation for Loggerithim is in the docs
subdirectory.  You can also find it in a more human-readable form at:

http://www.loggerithim.org

To install:

./configure
make
make install
make database
make certificates

If you use LR, or are at all interested in it, please subscribe to the mailing
lists. 

Thanks.

Cory 'G' Watson
gphat@loggerithim.org
